        "id": 5255
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-07-31T20:23:30Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "My guess is this is when the loop count is infinite. We use SkCodec::kRepetitionCountInfinite, which is -1, but the image stores that as 0.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 187,
        "startChar": 0,
