        "id": 5255
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-07-31T20:23:30Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We could definitely improve this by using ERRORF and SkCodec::ResultToString (which was added since this test was written), but it still doesn\u0027t have access to other interesting information, like the file that had the error.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 101,
